    a: "Yes. Wine cellar emergencies do not respect business hours and a $200,000+ collection at risk justifies after-hours dispatch. Our West Hollywood branch covers BH 7am-9pm Monday through Friday, 8am-7pm Saturday, 9am-5pm Sunday on standard service. After-hours and overnight emergency dispatch is available for active cellar failures with collection-at-risk; we charge a modest after-hours premium and we ask for a brief description of the failure and current cellar temperature when you call so we can match the right technician and parts inventory to the call. Call (323) 870-4790 anytime, voicemail rolls to the on-call dispatcher outside standard hours."
  },
