    <p><strong>Benedict Canyon.</strong> Mix of mid-century jewels and contemporary new-builds, generally 2,000-5,000 bottle cellars. WhisperKOOL Extreme 8000 and 15000 tii are dominant here, with some Wine Guardian on the larger estates. Canyon road access is straightforward; our West Hollywood truck reaches most BC addresses in 12-15 minutes.</p>

    <p><strong>Beverly Hills Flats.</strong> Pre-war homes remodeled extensively, with cellars typically built into modernized basements or main-floor walk-ins. Cellar size 1,500-3,000 bottles. Mix of WhisperKOOL Platinum, older Breezaire WKL, and newer CellarPro 4200VSx. Flat-grade access; service times are predictable.</p>

    <p><strong>North Beverly Hills.</strong> The largest lots and the largest cellars we work on, 5,000-10,000+ bottles, often Wine Guardian commercial-grade ducted systems with mechanical rooms separate from the cellar itself. Service is more involved (multi-zone access, longer diagnostic time) and we plan accordingly.</p>

